<th style="font-size:12px; background:#ccccff">Antiquity</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="font-size:12px">
<p><strong class="selflink">Nicaea I</strong>&#160;• <a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Constantinople" title="First Council of Constantinople">Constantinople I</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Ephesus" title="First Council of Ephesus">Ephesus</a> &#160;• <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Chalcedon" title="Council of Chalcedon">Chalcedon</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Constantinople" title="Second Council of Constantinople">Constantinople II</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Third_Council_of_Constantinople" title="Third Council of Constantinople">Constantinople III</a>&#160;• <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Nicaea" title="Second Council of Nicaea">Nicaea II</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Fourth_Council_of_Constantinople_(Catholic)" title="Fourth Council of Constantinople (Catholic)">Constantinople IV</a><br /></p>
