<a href="/wiki/Third_Council_of_the_Lateran" title="Third Council of the Lateran">Lateran III</a> &#160;• <a href="/wiki/Fourth_Council_of_the_Lateran" title="Fourth Council of the Lateran">Lateran IV</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Lyon" title="First Council of Lyon">Lyon I</a> &#160;• <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Lyon" title="Second Council of Lyon">Lyon II</a> &#160;• <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Vienne" title="Council of Vienne">Vienne</a><br /></p>
