<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Seven recognized in <a href="/wiki/Eastern_Orthodox_Church" title="Eastern Orthodox Church">East</a> and <a href="/wiki/Western_Christianity" title="Western Christianity">West</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><strong class="selflink">Nicaea I</strong> (325) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Constantinople" title="First Council of Constantinople">Constantinople I</a> (381) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/First_Council_of_Ephesus" title="First Council of Ephesus">Ephesus</a> (431) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Council_of_Chalcedon" title="Council of Chalcedon">Chalcedon</a> (451) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Constantinople" title="Second Council of Constantinople">Constantinople II</a> (553) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Third_Council_of_Constantinople" title="Third Council of Constantinople">Constantinople III</a> (680-681) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Second_Council_of_Nicaea" title="Second Council of Nicaea">Nicaea II</a> (787)</div>
</td>
