<tr>
<td class="navbox-abovebelow" style=";" colspan="2"><a href="/wiki/Anglicanism" title="Anglicanism">Anglicans</a> and most <a href="/wiki/Protestantism" title="Protestantism">Protestant churches</a> accept the first seven Ecumenical Councils.<br />
The <a href="/wiki/Oriental_Orthodoxy" title="Oriental Orthodoxy">Oriental Orthodox</a> accept the first three councils, the <a href="/wiki/Assyrian_Church_of_the_East" title="Assyrian Church of the East">Assyrian Church of the East</a> only the first two.</td>
